/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-01.md:31:- Action: shortlist at most four candidate NS-only structures, for example pressure-Hessian tensor algebra, strain-vorticity alignment identities, Lagrangian circulation or topology, or stochastic flow structure.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-004/planner-chains/chain-01.md:47:- Action: test the top candidates against the intended solution class, localization demands, and prior mission negatives.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:21:For exact rewrites of NS, there is a default expectation: once one restores localization, projection, and commutator bookkeeping, the same quadratic structure reappears. The chain knows this, but still treats reformulation as a live discovery direction instead of treating "collapse back to the same estimate" as the generic baseline that must be defeated by a sharply identified mechanism.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:27:The mission context is stronger than "the candidate uses an exact NS-looking feature." Tao's result blocks anything resting only on energy identity plus standard harmonic analysis. So the chain should demand a concrete statement of what the averaged model destroys and where that destruction enters the estimate. As written, a candidate can survive Step 1 by sounding algebraically special without showing that the specialness survives localization and actually matters quantitatively.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:51:- It never says which bottleneck is mission-central. Is it the De Giorgi truncated pressure contribution, a local-energy flux term, a vorticity stretching localization, or some projected interaction? Those are not interchangeable. A rewrite that helps one may do nothing for the others.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:54:- The Tao screen arrives too early and too weakly. Before the localization protocol is fixed, one cannot tell whether the candidate's supposedly NS-specific feature survives the actual estimate rather than only the bare identity.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:65:- The step still lacks a fixed localization protocol. "Where the localization cost lands" is not a minor detail. It is the whole question. If the cutoff, projector, and commutator placement are not frozen before the test, the candidate estimates are not being compared on equal terms.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:67:- The estimate table could flatten important distinctions. Two rewrites may share the same headline scaling but differ in where commutator costs, projector losses, or localization errors appear. If those are not itemized explicitly, the table will overstate sameness.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-01.md:79:- "Survive modest perturbation away from special alignment" is not operationally defined. Perturbation in what norm, on what scale, and relative to which localization? A cancellation can look robust or fragile depending on the metric.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:19:- The proposed target quantities are also too easy to game. "Critical-norm transfer" or "stretching-facing spectral production" can be named without any prior reason to think they survive localization, time integration, or cancellation.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:20:- "Define in advance what would count as a usable gain" sounds disciplined, but at this stage it is fake discipline. A gain that looks usable before localization and norm conversion often disappears once commutators, phase loss, or packet overlap are included.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:31:- The kill condition uses "same effective strength," but effective strength is undefined. Is that pointwise in the symbol? averaged over orientations? after frequency summation? after localization? after time averaging? Without that definition, the gate can be passed or failed by rhetoric.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:41:- A bounded shortlist may be too aggressive because the only nontrivial leverage, if any exists, may come from a hybrid mechanism: helical selection plus localization plus scenario-specific concentration geometry. The chain is organized as though a pure triad-level discriminator should appear first and only later be translated. That ordering likely excludes the only plausible successes.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:46:### Step 4 - Test whether the discriminator survives localization or scenario reduction
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:50:- Frequency-space helical statements are globally organized objects. Regularity arguments are local or at least localization-sensitive. The uncertainty-principle tax is not a detail here; it is likely the entire story.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:51:- By postponing localization until Step 4, the chain allows substantial effort to be spent on symbol-level structure that may have no physically local meaning. That is backwards. Localization should be near the front of the chain, not an after-the-fact feasibility check.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-003/attacks/chain-02.md:52:- "Scenario reduction" is vague. If the scenario is meant to stand in for a blowup mechanism, it must already be fixed sharply enough that one can say what localization means and what packets or regions are supposed to dominate.
